Instructions for Use

Step 1: Open a terminal (PowerShell or CMD)
pip install -r requirements.txt

Step 2: Add your Google OAuth credentials

Go to:
https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials

Create:
- OAuth client ID
- Authorized redirect URI: http://localhost:5000/callback

Step 3: Download the JSON as: client_secret.json
Place it in the project folder.

Step 4: Start the web app: python app.py

Step 5: Open the vault in your browser: http://localhost:5000/

