üîê Encrypt a File
- Login with Google
- Upload any file
- The app encrypts it using:
  -AES-256-GCM
  -RSA-4096 key wrapping

Only your account can decrypt it.

üîì Decrypt a File
Upload the .enc file and its .json metadata
App will unwrap the AES key
File is decrypted and downloaded
